ECB’s Bini Smaghi Says IMF Meeting Confirm Downside Risks

-- B y   G a b i   T h e s i n g
-- 
2011-09-25T14:17:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-25/ecb-s-bini-smaghi-says-imf-meeting-confirm-downside-risks.html
European Central Bank Executive
Board member Lorenzo Bini Smaghi said the IMF meetings
“confirmed what we said two weeks ago” that “there are
downside risks to the economy.” Bini Smaghi was speaking to
reporters in  Washington  today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gabi Thesing at 
 gthesing@bloomberg.net  